        <body>
            <div1 xml:id="d001" type="section" decls="#md" met="H">
                <head>
                    <title>1</title>
                    <abbr>1</abbr>
                    <bibl source="digital">Cristina Zanatta</bibl>
                </head>
                <div2 xml:id="001c001" type="carmen">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>1</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l1" n="">1.</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l2" n="1">Urbs opulenta viris et fertilis ubere glebae</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l3" n="2">Quam non Hybla thymo, non aequent palmite Thebae,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l4" n="3">Optima lina ferens Sacci nascentia Plebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l5" n="4">Fons insignis equis vel te vel Arione, Thebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l6" n="5">Cum pulsata vicem non possis reddere, debe.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l7" n="6">Nam si prisca tuis det tempora patribus Hebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l8" n="7">Et sit in ancipiti melior constantia plebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l9" n="8">Et socient animos sociantes labra, Cybebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l10" n="9">Nil Antenoridis oberit cum gurgite Phoebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l11" n="10">Immo salem coges intra sua limina, Phoebe.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l12" n="11">At tu qui patrio certas pro iure, Chorebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l13" n="12">Dulcis Aselle Lupo, virtutis amator ephebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l14" n="13">Qua potes, adversis obstantia pectora praebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l15" n="14">Te decet esse virum. Seu clamat copia be be,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l16" n="15">Si quid habes pulcrum chordis impelle, rebebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l17" n="16">Si nihil aut nostri carmen tibi displicet ebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l18" n="17">Sive latere velis clipeum, collectus in hebe,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l19" n="18">Cum reliquos hebetent turpia, turpis hebe.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="001c002" type="carmen">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>2</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l20" n="">2.</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l21" n="1">Lingua susurrantis, funesti schismatis est fax;</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l22" n="2">Veridici sermo, sapiens quem temperat, est pax.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l23" n="3">Quem Venus aut Bacchus aut alea decoquit, est fex:</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l24" n="4">Qui domat haec animo, moderati pectoris est rex.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l25" n="5">Effuge quem nosti vitiatum sordibus: est pix;</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l26" n="6">Elige quem cernis radiantem moribus: est nix.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l27" n="7">Si nitet in pravo facundia, civibus est nox;</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l28" n="8">In sapiente viro, patrii firmaminis est vox.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l29" n="9">Femina si fuerit mulier, tolerantibus est crux;</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l30" n="10">Si fuerit phoenix, domui mirabilis est lux.</l>
                </div2>
            </div1>
            <div1 xml:id="d002" type="section" decls="#md" met="H">
                <head>
                    <title>2</title>
                    <abbr>2</abbr>
                    <bibl source="digital">Cristina Zanatta</bibl>
                </head>
                <div2 xml:id="002c001" type="responsio">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>1</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d002l1" n="tit.">Mussatus</p>
                    <l xml:id="d002l2" n="1">Tu qui nostra soles dubiis absolvere curis</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l3" n="2">Pectora, venturi cui mens non inscia fati,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l4" n="3">Uranie dictante tua, da cernere quidnam</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l5" n="4">Immineat nostrae, Tuscos si vicerit, urbi,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l6" n="5">Iste carens terra Carolus. Stat fabula coram</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l7" n="6">Ignavo quid cessit equo post facta dolenti,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l8" n="7">Sessorem qui sponte tulit quo vinceret hostem:</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l9" n="8">Vicit et occubuit pro libertate relicta.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l10" n="9">Quod si casus eat victis ut Tuscia Gallis</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l11" n="10">Plus aequo exultet, caput et gens improba tollat</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l12" n="11">Utrices meditata vices, timor imminet altus</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l13" n="12">Ne cadat in nostros candens discessio cives.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="002c002" type="carmen">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>2</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d002l14" n="tit.">Lovatus</p>
                    <l xml:id="d002l15" n="1">Quae sors immineat patriae si Francia Tuscos</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l16" n="2">Vicerit aut victis exultet Etruria Gallis,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l17" n="3">Consulis, eventus dubii servator Aselle.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l18" n="4">Certus in incerto non sum, prudentia menti</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l19" n="5">Tanta meae non est: non me sic implet Apollo</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l20" n="6">Divinusque tepor, sed, quod per tempora vidi,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l21" n="7">Forsitan occulti res est praesaga futuri.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l22" n="8">Vidi ego, cui placui, fuerat dum parvus, amicum</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l23" n="9">In damnum crevisse meum: cum surgit in altum</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l24" n="10">Fortunatus inops humilem contemnit amantem.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l25" n="11">Vidi ego, cum placidus retinet suus alveus amnes,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l26" n="12">Purpureos circum flores et gramine picto</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l27" n="13">Luxuriare solum; tumeant si forte malignis</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l28" n="14">Imbribus aut alios admittant flumina fontes,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l29" n="15">Sordet humus dilecta prius faciemque virentem</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l30" n="16">Perdit et immani squallent sub gurgite ripae.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l31" n="17">Parva fuit tellus et Longa mitior Alba</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l32" n="18">Quae nunc imperii caput est et legibus orbem</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l33" n="19">Temperat. Alluvium timeo viresque potentum:</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l34" n="20">Regis enim virtus flatu provecta secundo</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l35" n="21">Est bona finitimis, ut Romulus ante Sabinis,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l36" n="22">Tullus ut Albano, Nano velut hospita Phocis.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l37" n="23">Rursus ut aspexi quid pristina pertulit aetas,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l38" n="24">Qua veterum culpa, quis cives cladibus olim</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l39" n="25">Spiritus impegit, quorum reparata labore</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l40" n="26">Libertas immota viget quantumque pericli</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l41" n="27">Sit bene composito pulcram refricare quietem,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l42" n="28">Ascensu vereor Tusci ne gentis amicae</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l43" n="29">Descensu nostram dissensibus inquinet urbem.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l44" n="30">Ergo ego cum Franci timeam, cum regna Suevi,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l45" n="31">Cum mea tam vario nutet mens anxia fluctu,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l46" n="32">Hinc Boreae furiis, hinc turbine territus Austri</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l47" n="33">Sanius eligerem nulli dare carbasa vento,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d002l48" n="34">Si tamen alterutra labi nos parte necesse est.</l>
                </div2>
            </div1>
